               <msContents>
                  <summary>Book of Order of the Disciples, መጽሐፈ: ሥርዓቶሙ: ለሐዋርያት, incipit, በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ: ዝንቱ: መጽሐፈ: ሥርዓቶሙ ለሐዋርያት: ወባዕዳንሂ: እም: ፸ ወ ፱ አርድዕት:  ንኡሳን: ወዘኮነ: ኵሎ: እምዜናሆሙ:, arranged in eighteen sections: section 1, introduction, f<locus target="#1r"/>-14v; section 2, about Peter, f<locus target="#14v"/>-20v; section 3, about Simon, son of Cleapas, f<locus target="#20v"/>-23v; section 4, about James, the brother of Jesus, f<locus target="#23v"/>-29v; section 5, about Bartholomew, f<locus target="#29v"/>-39r; section 6, about Matthew, the Evangelist, f<locus target="#39v"/>-51r; section 7, about Luke, the evangelist, f<locus target="#51v"/>-55r); section 8, about Philip, the Apostle, f<locus target="#55v"/>-63r; section 9, about Andrew, the Apostle, f<locus target="#63v"/>-73r; section 10, about Andrew and Bartholomew, f<locus target="#73r"/>-90r; section 11, about Andrew, f<locus target="#90r"/>-93r; section 12, about John, the Evangelist, f<locus target="#93v"/>-113r; section 13, about James, son of Alpheas, f<locus target="#113v"/>-114v; section 14, about Matthias, the Apostle, f<locus target="#114v"/>-127v; section 15, about James, son of Zebedee, brother of John, f<locus target="#127v"/>-133r; section 16, about Mark, the Evangelist, f<locus target="#133v"/>-137r; section 17, about Thomas, the Apostle, f<locus target="#137v"/>-154v.; section 18, about Jude, the brother of Jesus, and Thaddeus, the Apostle, <locus target="#154v"/>, incomplete at the end.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
